<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{company.name}} - Fiyat Teklifi {{proposalNo}}</title>
<style>
  @page {
    size: A4;
    margin: 0;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  html, body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    color: #1A2332;
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    line-height: 1.5;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .page {
    width: 210mm;
    height: 297mm;
    page-break-after: always;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page:last-child {
    page-break-after: auto;
  }

  /* ==================== COVER ==================== */
  .cover {
    background: #0A1628;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 22mm 20mm;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .cover::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120mm;
    right: -120mm;
    width: 280mm;
    height: 280mm;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 255, 240, 0.18) 0%, rgba(115, 171, 255, 0.08) 40%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .cover::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80mm;
    left: -80mm;
    width: 200mm;
    height: 200mm;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(115, 171, 255, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .cover-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .cover-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .cover-logo {
    width: 48mm;
  }

  .cover-meta {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cover-meta .label {
    font-size: 7.5pt;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 1mm;
  }

  .cover-meta .value {
    color: #FFFFFF;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 3mm;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: none;
    font-size: 10pt;
  }

  .cover-title-block {
    margin-top: 60mm;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .cover-eyebrow {
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #00FFF0;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 6mm;
  }

  .cover-title {
    font-size: 48pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 10mm;
  }

  .cover-title .accent {
    color: #00FFF0;
  }

  .cover-for {
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 3mm;
  }

  .cover-customer {
    font-size: 20pt;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding-bottom: 4mm;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: 8mm;
    display: inline-block;
    min-width: 90mm;
  }

  .cover-greeting {
    margin-top: 8mm;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 130mm;
  }

  .cover-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    padding-top: 8mm;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .cover-footer .company {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 9pt;
  }

  /* ==================== CONTENT PAGES ==================== */
  .content {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 18mm 20mm 18mm 20mm;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .page-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-bottom: 6mm;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
    margin-bottom: 10mm;
  }

  .page-header-logo {
    width: 28mm;
  }

  .page-header-info {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 8pt;
    color: #5A6878;
  }

  .page-header-info strong {
    color: #1A2332;
    display: block;
    font-size: 9pt;
    margin-bottom: 0.5mm;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 20pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A1628;
    margin-bottom: 2mm;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    color: #5A6878;
    margin-bottom: 6mm;
  }

  /* ==================== PRICE TABLE ==================== */
  .price-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 9.5pt;
    margin-bottom: 8mm;
  }

  .price-table thead tr {
    background: #0A1628;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .price-table thead th {
    padding: 3.5mm 3mm;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 9pt;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .price-table thead th.num {
    text-align: right;
  }

  .price-table tbody td {
    padding: 4mm 3mm;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
    vertical-align: top;
    min-height: 8mm;
  }

  .price-table tbody td.num {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .price-table tbody tr.empty td {
    color: #C5CCD6;
    font-style: italic;
    height: 10mm;
  }

  .price-table .col-item {
    width: 50%;
  }

  .price-table .col-qty {
    width: 12%;
  }

  .price-table .col-unit {
    width: 18%;
  }

  .price-table .col-total {
    width: 20%;
  }

  .price-table tfoot td {
    padding: 3mm 3mm;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
  }

  .price-table tfoot .subtotal td {
    color: #5A6878;
  }

  .price-table tfoot .discount td {
    color: #5A6878;
  }

  .price-table tfoot .grand-total td {
    background: #F7F9FC;
    color: #0A1628;
    font-size: 12pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4.5mm 3mm;
    border: none;
    border-top: 2px solid #0A1628;
  }

  .price-table tfoot .monthly td {
    color: #5A6878;
    font-size: 9pt;
    padding-top: 4mm;
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px dashed #E5EAF0;
  }

  .price-hint {
    background: #F7F9FC;
    border-left: 3px solid #73ABFF;
    padding: 3mm 4mm;
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: #5A6878;
    margin-bottom: 6mm;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .price-hint strong {
    color: #0A1628;
  }

  /* ==================== TERMS PAGE ==================== */
  .terms-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .term-block {
    padding: 2.5mm 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
  }

  .term-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .term-title {
    font-size: 10pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A1628;
    margin-bottom: 1.2mm;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2.5mm;
  }

  .term-title::before {
    content: '';
    width: 3.5mm;
    height: 0.8mm;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #73ABFF 0%, #00FFF0 100%);
    border-radius: 1mm;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .term-body {
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: #3A4758;
    line-height: 1.55;
    padding-left: 6mm;
  }

  .term-body p + p {
    margin-top: 1mm;
  }

  /* ==================== TANITIM SAYFASI ==================== */
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #73ABFF;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4mm;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 22pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A1628;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 5mm;
    max-width: 150mm;
  }

  .hero-title .accent {
    color: #00D4CE;
  }

  .hero-intro {
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #3A4758;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12mm;
    max-width: 155mm;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 7mm 6mm;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 13mm;
    height: 13mm;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 4mm;
  }

  .feature-icon svg {
    width: 6.5mm;
    height: 6.5mm;
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-size: 10.5pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A1628;
    margin-bottom: 2mm;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    color: #5A6878;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  /* ==================== LUNASPOT TANITIM ==================== */
  .lunaspot-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 6mm;
    padding: 6mm 8mm;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1628 0%, #1a1a3e 100%);
    border-radius: 3mm;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .lunaspot-hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -40mm;
    right: -40mm;
    width: 90mm;
    height: 90mm;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139, 107, 255, 0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .lunaspot-logo {
    height: 18mm;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .lunaspot-features .feature-card {
    padding: 5mm;
    border: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
    border-radius: 2.5mm;
  }

  /* ==================== MODÜLLER SAYFASI ==================== */
  .modules-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5mm;
    margin-bottom: 6mm;
  }

  .module-card {
    border: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
    border-radius: 2mm;
    padding: 2.5mm 3mm 2.5mm 3mm;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 2.5mm;
  }

  .module-icon {
    width: 7mm;
    height: 7mm;
    min-width: 7mm;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .module-icon svg {
    width: 3.8mm;
    height: 3.8mm;
  }

  .module-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .module-title {
    font-size: 8.5pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0A1628;
    margin-bottom: 0.5mm;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .module-desc {
    font-size: 7pt;
    color: #5A6878;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Combined page section divider */
  .section-divider {
    border-top: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
    margin: 4mm 0 5mm 0;
  }

  /* ==================== FOOTER ==================== */
  .page-footer {
    position: absolute;
    left: 20mm;
    right: 20mm;
    bottom: 10mm;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 7.5pt;
    color: #8A95A5;
    padding-top: 4mm;
    border-top: 1px solid #E5EAF0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .page-footer .left {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6mm;
  }

  .page-footer strong {
    color: #1A2332;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ========================================================= -->
<!-- PAGE 1: COVER                                              -->
<!-- ========================================================= -->
<div class="page cover">
  <div class="cover-inner">
    <div class="cover-header">
      <img src="{{{assets.logoWhite}}}" class="cover-logo" alt="Novem">
      <div class="cover-meta">
        <div class="label">Teklif No</div>
        <div class="value">{{proposalNo}}</div>
        <div class="label">Tarih</div>
        <div class="value">{{formatDate date}}</div>
        <div class="label">Revizyon</div>
        <div class="value">{{revision}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-title-block">
      <div class="cover-eyebrow">Proje Teklifi</div>
      <div class="cover-title">
        {{title.main}}{{#if title.accent}}<br><span class="accent">{{title.accent}}</span>{{/if}}
      </div>

      <div class="cover-for">Hazırlanan</div>
      <div class="cover-customer">{{customer.tradeName}}{{#if customer.contactPerson}} — {{customer.contactPerson}}{{/if}}</div>

      <div class="cover-greeting">
        Sayın {{greetingNameOrContact customer}},<br><br>
        Firmamızdan teklif almak sureti ile gösterdiğiniz ilgiye teşekkür ederiz.
        İşletmeniz için hazırladığımız {{title.main}} çözümüne ait detayları ilerleyen sayfalarda bulabilirsiniz.
        Her türlü soru ve önerileriniz için değerli dönüşlerinizi bekleriz.<br><br>
        Saygılarımızla.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-footer">
      <div>
        <div class="company">{{company.name}}</div>
        <div>{{company.address}}</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        {{company.tax}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========================================================= -->
<!-- PAGE 2: NOVEM POS TANITIM                                  -->
<!-- ========================================================= -->
<div class="page content">
  <div class="page-header">
    <img src="{{{assets.logoDark}}}" class="page-header-logo" alt="Novem">
    <div class="page-header-info">
      <strong>{{customer.tradeName}}{{#if customer.contactPerson}} — {{customer.contactPerson}}{{/if}}</strong>
      Teklif No: {{proposalNo}} · {{formatDate date}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-eyebrow">Ürün Tanıtımı</div>
  <div class="hero-title">Novem <span class="accent">POS</span> ile restoran yönetimini baştan tanımlayın.</div>
  <div class="hero-intro">
    Tüm sipariş, servis ve operasyon süreçlerinizi tek çatı altında toplayan entegre ve bulut tabanlı sistemimizle hız, kontrol ve verimlilik sizinle. Satışlarınızı, ürün performanslarını ve ödeme yöntemlerini anlık olarak takip edin; gelişmiş analiz araçlarıyla hangi ürünün ne zaman daha çok sattığını görün, stok ve maliyet planlamanızı veriye dayalı kararlarla yönetin.
  </div>

  <div class="features-grid">

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon" style="background:#00D4CE">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="2" y1="10" x2="22" y2="10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-title">Çoklu Ödeme Seçenekleri</div>
      <div class="feature-desc">Nakit, kredi kartı, yemek kartları ve QR dahil olmak üzere tüm ödeme yöntemlerini tek bir ekranda yönetin.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon" style="background:#4A6FE3">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 007.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 00-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 00-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 007.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-title">Güçlü Entegrasyon Desteği</div>
      <div class="feature-desc">Yemeksepeti, Trendyol ve Getir gibi pazaryerlerinden gelen siparişler Novem POS'a otomatik aktarılır, operasyonel süreçler sadeleşir.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon" style="background:#73ABFF">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 109 20h9a5 5 0 000-10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-title">Bulut Tabanlı ve Çevrimdışı Erişim</div>
      <div class="feature-desc">Bulut tabanlı güvenli erişim ile verilerinize her yerden ulaşın; internet olmasa bile kesintisiz çalışmaya devam edin.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon" style="background:#8B5FE8">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V6l-3-4z"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 01-8 0"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-title">Çoklu Satış Kanalları Yönetimi</div>
      <div class="feature-desc">Restoran içi satışlardan online siparişlere kadar; her kanal Novem POS ile tek çatı altında birleşir.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon" style="background:#FF6B6B">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 01-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 010 2.82z"/><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="1" fill="#FFFFFF" stroke="none"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-title">Ürün Yönetimi</div>
      <div class="feature-desc">Ürün reçetesi yönetimi ile işletmenizin ürün yaşam döngüsünü baştan sona kontrol edebilir, veri odaklı kararlar alabilirsiniz.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon" style="background:#10D9C4">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-title">Detaylı ve Dinamik Stok Takibi</div>
      <div class="feature-desc">Ürün bazında giriş-çıkış takibi, minimum stok uyarıları ve anlık maliyet analiziyle stok yönetimini otomatikleştirin.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="page-footer">
    <div class="left">
      <span><strong>Novem Yazılım</strong></span>
      <span>{{company.tax}}</span>
    </div>
    <div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========================================================= -->
<!-- PAGE 3: MODÜLLER + LUNASPOT (yarı yarıya)                  -->
<!-- ========================================================= -->
<div class="page content">
  <div class="page-header">
    <img src="{{{assets.logoDark}}}" class="page-header-logo" alt="Novem">
    <div class="page-header-info">
      <strong>{{customer.tradeName}}{{#if customer.contactPerson}} — {{customer.contactPerson}}{{/if}}</strong>
      Teklif No: {{proposalNo}} · {{formatDate date}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-title" style="font-size:16pt;">Novem POS Modülleri</div>
  <div class="section-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:4mm;">İhtiyaçlarınıza göre seçebileceğiniz, birbirine entegre çalışan modüler yapı</div>

  <div class="modules-grid">

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#0A1628">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="5" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="2" y1="10" x2="22" y2="10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem Kasa</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Hızlı ödeme alma, anlık masa takibi ve entegrasyonlarla satışın kalbi.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#00D4CE">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><path d="M14 14h3v3"/><path d="M14 19h3"/><path d="M19 14v3"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem QR</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Yapay zekâ destekli çoklu dil, alerjen uyarıları ve dijital menü deneyimi.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#73ABFF">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 8a6 6 0 0112 0c0 7 3 9 3 9H3s3-2 3-9"/><path d="M10.3 21a1.94 1.94 0 003.4 0"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem Servis</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Sipariş alımını hızlandırıp servis süreçlerini kusursuzlaştıran çözüm.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#FF6B6B">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 13.87A4 4 0 017.41 6a5.11 5.11 0 011.05-1.54 5 5 0 017.08 0A5.11 5.11 0 0116.59 6 4 4 0 0118 13.87V21H6z"/><line x1="6" y1="17" x2="18" y2="17"/></svg>
