      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#8B5FE8">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 16H9m10 0h3v-3.15a1 1 0 00-.84-.99L16 11l-2.7-3.6a1 1 0 00-.8-.4H5.24a2 2 0 00-1.8 1.1l-.8 1.63A6 6 0 002 12.42V16h2"/><circle cx="6.5" cy="16.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="16.5" cy="16.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem Park</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Vale hizmetini dijitalleştiren, misafir memnuniyetini artıran altyapı.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#10D9C4">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem Patron</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Tüm operasyonel verileri tek mobil platformda yöneticiye sunar.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#00D4FF">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem Online</div>
        <div class="module-desc">7/24 açık dijital kapı sunan online sipariş sistemi.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#FFB84A">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12" y2="18.01"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Novem Self</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Misafirler kasa sırası beklemeden siparişini kendisi oluşturur.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <div class="lunaspot-hero" style="padding:4mm 6mm; margin-bottom:4mm;">
    <img src="{{{assets.lunaspotWhite}}}" class="lunaspot-logo" style="height:13mm;" alt="Lunaspot">
  </div>

  <div class="section-eyebrow" style="color:#8b6bff; margin-bottom:2mm;">Hotspot Çözümü</div>
  <div class="hero-title" style="font-size:14pt; margin-bottom:2.5mm; max-width:165mm;">
    Toplu yaşam alanlarında <span class="accent" style="color:#8b6bff">internetinizi</span> güvenle yönetin.
  </div>
  <div class="hero-intro" style="font-size:8.5pt; margin-bottom:5mm; line-height:1.55;">
    KVKK uyumlu, 5651 sayılı kanun çerçevesinde log imzalı, Router tabanlı profesyonel hotspot çözümü.
  </div>

  <div class="modules-grid">

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#5aa7ff">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Hızlı ve Stabil</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Kesintisiz internet deneyimi için optimize edilmiş altyapı.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#8b6bff">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">%100 Yasal</div>
        <div class="module-desc">5651 sayılı kanuna uygun loglama ve zaman damgası.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="module-card">
      <div class="module-icon" style="background:#c58bff">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="module-text">
        <div class="module-title">Kolay Yönetim</div>
        <div class="module-desc">Tek panelden yüzlerce cihazı ve kullanıcıyı yönetin.</div>
